        "title": "Collect Props from attic",
        "description": "<p>Heya @[{\"type\":\"person\",\"id\":\"686717\",\"label\":\"Liam Mills\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://files.productive.io/people/avatars/35cb750c-e488-45e6-86b7-5c42af8f248c/thumb/aaa.jpg\",\"attachment_url\":null,\"is_done\":false}] </p><p>If you are in the office today, was hoping you could pop up into the attic to grab the Hunter Water props?</p><p>Should be a basket or similar or blue towels and bathroom type accessories? Potentially a hunter water bucket.</p><p></p><p>Tay and I are out this morning sourcing wardrobe and props but let us know if you have any questions!</p><p></p><p>Thanks!!</p>",
